Huan Er!

4
00:00:38,439 --> 00:00:41,040
It's time to go.

5
00:00:41,040 --> 00:00:42,959
I'm coming.

6
00:00:48,479 --> 00:00:51,259
Goodbye, Da Huang!

7
00:01:24,360 --> 00:01:33,650
 ­  

8
00:01:40,439 --> 00:01:44,139
- Is that the one? 
 - Yes. That's her.

9
00:01:44,139 --> 00:01:46,359
Yi Fan!

10
00:01:48,200 --> 00:01:50,519
Mister, stop the car here.

11
00:01:50,519 --> 00:01:52,339
Yi Fan!

12
00:01:53,800 --> 00:01:56,100
- Mister, turn the car around. 
 - Thanks, Mister.

13
00:01:56,100 --> 00:01:58,900
- The house is just over there. 
 - All right, no problem.

14
00:01:58,900 --> 00:02:02,380
Yi Fan! It's been so many years.

15
00:02:02,380 --> 00:02:03,590
I'll help you get the key.

16
00:02:03,590 --> 00:02:05,079
- Let's go. 
 - Okay.

17
00:02:05,079 --> 00:02:06,920
Huan Er, do you remember Aunt Lin Yi Fan?

18
00:02:06,920 --> 00:02:09,860
She used to hold you when you were little.

19
00:02:09,860 --> 00:02:11,420
- Say hello. 
 - Hello, Aunt Yi Fan.

20
00:02:11,420 --> 00:02:12,260
She doesn't remember.

21
00:02:12,260 --> 00:02:14,360
She was so little back then. How could she remember?

22
00:02:14,360 --> 00:02:16,140
This way.

23
00:02:17,660 --> 00:02:20,600
No problem. I'll finish the paperwork before I get off work.

24
00:02:20,600 --> 00:02:22,700
- Thank you. See you later. 
 - Okay.

25
00:02:22,700 --> 00:02:25,200
Huan Er, I'm going to the hospital. Watch over things for me.

26
00:02:25,200 --> 00:02:28,140
- Li Na, I'll go with you. 
 - Okay, Yi Fan.

27
00:02:53,779 --> 00:02:56,160
Watch my stuff for me.

28
00:03:33,939 --> 00:03:35,819
Hey...

29
00:03:37,740 --> 00:03:40,280
There's bird poop on your head.

30
00:03:49,939 --> 00:03:52,660
Here. Use this to wipe it off.

31
00:03:53,719 --> 00:03:55,879
Thanks.

32
00:03:58,740 --> 00:03:59,760
Did you just move in?

33
00:03:59,760 --> 00:04:01,860
I haven't seen you before.

34
00:04:02,580 --> 00:04:06,280
My home is right here. I guess we're neighbors now.

35
00:04:06,280 --> 00:04:07,980
Thanks. Nice to meet you.

36
00:04:07,980 --> 00:04:10,120
- My name is— 
 - Bye-bye.

37
00:04:14,860 --> 00:04:18,580
 This guy... why is he so weird? 

38
00:04:25,219 --> 00:04:27,020
 My name is Chen Huan Er. 

39
00:04:27,020 --> 00:04:29,020
 I'm sixteen years old. 

40
00:04:29,020 --> 00:04:34,000
 Before this, I lived in Sishui County, on the far west side of Tianhe. 

41
00:04:34,000 --> 00:04:36,140
 Don't underestimate me just because I come from a small town. 

42
00:04:36,140 --> 00:04:41,079
 I'm fully confident that I can handle this new chapter in my life. 

43
00:04:41,079 --> 00:04:46,080
 After all, when I was a kid, I had my share of big moments. 

44
00:04:46,080 --> 00:04:48,023
 Let's all congratulate Chen Huan Er. 
   

45
00:04:48,023 --> 00:04:52,100
 She overcame every challenge, performed outstandingly in this academic competition, 

46
00:04:52,100 --> 00:04:54,299
 and won the title of "Star of Sishui." 
   

47
00:04:54,299 --> 00:04:57,619
 Chen Huan Er, tell us how you feel. 

48
00:04:58,020 --> 00:05:01,020
 I... I'm so excited. 

49
00:05:01,020 --> 00:05:02,959
 Louder. 

50
00:05:03,380 --> 00:05:05,440
 I... I'm so excited! 

51
00:05:05,440 --> 00:05:06,879
 Excited about what? 
   

52
00:05:06,879 --> 00:05:11,519
 Excited to become... the Flower of Sishui. 

53
00:05:14,200 --> 00:05:16,060
I was young back then.

54
00:05:16,060 --> 00:05:18,940
But now, I definitely won't stumble over my words.

55
00:05:18,940 --> 00:05:23,280
 Tianhe No. 1 High School, get ready to welcome the Star of Sishui. 

56
00:05:30,690 --> 00:05:31,820
Students.

57
00:05:31,820 --> 00:05:33,480
- Everyone— 
 - Quiet down.

58
00:05:33,480 --> 00:05:34,859
Settle down.

59
00:05:34,859 --> 00:05:37,279
I have an announcement.

60
00:05:37,279 --> 00:05:39,240
Our class has a new student.

61
00:05:39,240 --> 00:05:41,639
Her name is Chen Huan Er.

62
00:05:41,639 --> 00:05:46,299
Everyone's busy studying, so I won’t give a long introduction.

63
00:05:46,940 --> 00:05:49,600
Chen Huan Er, there's an empty seat in the second-to-last row.

64
00:05:49,600 --> 00:05:52,739
- You can sit there. 
 - Okay, sir.

65
00:05:53,959 --> 00:05:57,299
You guys, get to know each other after class.

66
00:06:07,380 --> 00:06:08,779
- Hello. 
 - Hey, new girl!

67
00:06:08,779 --> 00:06:12,099
Hello, I'm the class president. Just call me Xin Yan.

68
00:06:12,099 --> 00:06:14,460
Where did you transfer from?

69
00:06:15,020 --> 00:06:16,020
Sishui.

70
00:06:16,020 --> 00:06:18,180
Where's Sishui? Out of town?

71
00:06:18,180 --> 00:06:20,900
Sishui is a county.

72
00:06:21,519 --> 00:06:23,280
Never heard of it.

73
00:06:23,280 --> 00:06:24,900
You're just bad at geography.

74
00:06:24,900 --> 00:06:27,300
It's the county on the far west side.

75
00:06:33,199 --> 00:06:35,460
Class, stand up!

76
00:06:35,460 --> 00:06:38,950
 Good morning, teacher! 

77
00:06:38,950 --> 00:06:41,680
Good morning, students. Please sit down.

78
00:06:43,079 --> 00:06:47,240
Students, for this month's exam we will only cover up to Required Course 3,

79
00:06:47,240 --> 00:06:50,200
so in this class I won't review previous topics.

80
00:06:50,200 --> 00:06:52,959
Let's get straight into the trigonometric functions of arbitrary angles.

81
00:06:52,959 --> 00:06:56,260
Please open your math textbooks to page 53.

82
00:07:03,560 --> 00:07:07,160
Students, we've covered these key points, tricky parts, and exam topics

83
00:07:07,160 --> 00:07:08,920
in the previous lessons.

84
00:07:08,920 --> 00:07:12,960
Today, we'll mainly discuss... 
    

85
00:07:12,960 --> 00:07:15,279
how the x-coordinate stretches to four times its original length,

86
00:07:15,279 --> 00:07:18,000
 while the y-coordinate remains unchanged. 

87
00:07:36,879 --> 00:07:41,360
Hey, why aren't you guys eating in the cafeteria?

88
00:07:41,360 --> 00:07:43,440
The school doesn't have a cafeteria.

89
00:07:44,079 --> 00:07:47,220
Then where can I buy food outside?

90
00:07:47,220 --> 00:07:49,400
You didn't bring lunch?

91
00:07:55,440 --> 00:07:57,880
Let's go buy lunch together.

92
00:07:58,519 --> 00:08:00,079
Isn't that not enough food?

93
00:08:00,079 --> 00:08:02,639
Not for both of us. Let's go.

94
00:08:05,140 --> 00:08:08,040
By the way, I still don't know your name.

95
00:08:08,040 --> 00:08:09,839
Qi Qi.

96
00:08:10,560 --> 00:08:13,179
Bring me a meat sandwich while you're out.

97
00:08:13,179 --> 00:08:15,380
- Get it yourself. 
 - I have training.

98
00:08:15,380 --> 00:08:18,140
Just bring it over when you're done. Thanks.

99
00:08:22,040 --> 00:08:24,190
Jing Xi Chi. Our class's sports committee member.

100
00:08:24,190 --> 00:08:26,180
Sports committee?

101
00:08:26,920 --> 00:08:29,434
No wonder he looks so athletic.

102
00:08:29,434 --> 00:08:31,514
Do you guys know each other?

103
00:08:32,539 --> 00:08:34,600
No.

104
00:08:34,600 --> 00:08:38,680
You've been so quiet all morning. I thought you were shy.

105
00:08:41,065 --> 00:08:43,885
What kind of competition is the "Flower of Sishui"?

106
00:08:45,419 --> 00:08:48,100
I saw the note you wrote this morning.

107
00:08:48,960 --> 00:08:50,780
It's just a local academic competition.

108
00:08:50,780 --> 00:08:53,780
Actually, it's called the "Star of Sishui," not the "Flower of Sishui."

109
00:08:53,780 --> 00:08:57,800
I heard students from the suburban county areas are all really smart.

110
00:08:57,800 --> 00:08:59,979
Are students from your area all academic geniuses?

111
00:08:59,979 --> 00:09:01,879
Where did you hear that rumor?

112
00:09:01,879 --> 00:09:04,799
I get it. You top students are all so modest.

113
00:09:04,799 --> 00:09:07,399
To be honest, my grades are a mess.

114
00:09:07,399 --> 00:09:09,419
Can you help a desk mate out?

115
00:09:09,419 --> 00:09:11,700
No, you've got the wrong idea.

116
00:09:11,700 --> 00:09:15,019
I... I'm really not that smart.

117
00:09:18,100 --> 00:09:23,080
The Flower of Sishui... I'm counting on you for tomorrow's exam.

118
00:09:24,380 --> 00:09:28,981
   

119
00:09:28,981 --> 00:09:31,390
   

120
00:09:31,390 --> 00:09:33,420
The new girl and her desk mate really are a perfect match.

121
00:09:33,420 --> 00:09:37,240
One ranked dead last, the other second to last.

122
00:09:37,240 --> 00:09:40,490
Look. Li Tian is in first place again.

123
00:09:49,980 --> 00:09:52,420
   

124
00:09:53,780 --> 00:09:56,020
   

125
00:09:58,960 --> 00:10:01,519
Sorry, Qi Qi.

126
00:10:02,120 --> 00:10:06,060
If you hadn't copied from me, you wouldn't have ended up like this.

127
00:10:07,880 --> 00:10:09,345
Qi Qi.

128
00:10:09,345 --> 00:10:11,225
I'm sorry.

129
00:10:11,960 --> 00:10:14,340
I accidentally did too well.

130
00:10:14,340 --> 00:10:19,360
If I had scored just a little lower, our names would have been right next to each other.

131
00:10:20,680 --> 00:10:24,420
Huan Er, Qi Qi, and the sports representative. The homeroom teacher wants to see you.

132
00:10:28,860 --> 00:10:30,340
Qi Qi.

133
00:10:30,340 --> 00:10:33,000
What should I even say to you?

134
00:10:33,000 --> 00:10:37,960
If you're going to copy answers, at least be a bit more discerning.

135
00:10:37,960 --> 00:10:41,600
Her answers were completely wrong. Didn't you even notice?

136
00:10:41,600 --> 00:10:44,840
Always trying to be clever.

137
00:10:48,179 --> 00:10:50,440
Chen Huan Er...

138
00:10:50,440 --> 00:10:51,879
This doesn't add up.

139
00:10:51,879 --> 00:10:56,799
Your mom told me that back in your old school your grades were pretty good.

140
00:10:56,799 --> 00:11:00,320
So why is it that now you don't even know the basics?

141
00:11:01,260 --> 00:11:03,699
Give me your parents' phone number.

142
00:11:04,639 --> 00:11:06,939
I need to call and ask.

143
00:11:06,939 --> 00:11:08,779
But sir...

144
00:11:09,519 --> 00:11:11,800
And you.

145
00:11:22,159 --> 00:11:24,000
You did well this time.

146
00:11:24,000 --> 00:11:25,799
Keep it up.

147
00:11:25,799 --> 00:11:29,480
Whether our class average improves depends on you.

148
00:11:29,480 --> 00:11:31,000
Okay.

149
00:11:31,000 --> 00:11:32,799
Don't worry, sir.

150
00:11:32,799 --> 00:11:36,110
From now on, I won't be ranked last again.

151
00:11:40,020 --> 00:11:41,399
Don't just stand there.

152
00:11:41,399 --> 00:11:44,339
- Get to class. 
 - Bye, sir.

153
00:11:46,720 --> 00:11:48,360
Jing Xi Chi.

154
00:11:48,360 --> 00:11:50,960
- Keep it up. 
 - Got it, sir.

155
00:12:09,399 --> 00:12:10,939
 Off to a bad start. 

156
00:12:10,939 --> 00:12:13,220
 I have to go all out now. 

157
00:12:15,039 --> 00:12:18,320
Mom...

158
00:12:21,440 --> 00:12:23,480
I'm sorry.

159
00:12:23,480 --> 00:12:26,540
I totally messed up my exam.

160
00:12:27,179 --> 00:12:31,440
The school might call you.

161
00:12:31,440 --> 00:12:34,559
I'm sorry.

162
00:12:39,020 --> 00:12:42,400
 Not bad. My acting skills are still sharp. 

163
00:12:52,039 --> 00:12:54,120
 The Flower of Sishui is back. 

164
00:12:54,120 --> 00:12:58,540
 Go wash up and eat. I bought your favorite salt-baked chicken. 

165
00:13:12,039 --> 00:13:13,779
Oh no...

166
00:13:13,779 --> 00:13:16,280
What if I can't cry?

167
00:13:23,960 --> 00:13:26,419
Mom...

168
00:13:27,879 --> 00:13:30,639
I'm sorry.

169
00:13:30,639 --> 00:13:32,480
I failed the exam.

170
00:13:32,480 --> 00:13:36,540
If you can't cry, don't force it. Don't waste water. Your teacher called.

171
00:13:41,960 --> 00:13:43,880
Come and eat.

172
00:13:44,600 --> 00:13:46,740
I didn't cry.

173
00:13:46,740 --> 00:13:47,919
Nope.

174
00:13:47,919 --> 00:13:49,679
Good, then.

175
00:13:50,331 --> 00:13:52,431
Sit down and eat.

176
00:13:56,039 --> 00:13:57,680
Here.

177
00:14:00,159 --> 00:14:02,620
It's not a big deal, right?

178
00:14:02,620 --> 00:14:04,179
School is tough.

179
00:14:04,179 --> 00:14:07,639
Having classmates who are better than you is a good thing.

180
00:14:07,639 --> 00:14:09,960
The Flower of Sishui can't just wither so easily.

181
00:14:09,960 --> 00:14:11,980
Here, eat more.

182
00:14:13,340 --> 00:14:16,679
I'm a wilted flower now.

183
00:14:16,679 --> 00:14:19,600
What wilted flower? You're still a budding blossom.

184
00:14:19,600 --> 00:14:22,080
All right, enough drama. Hurry up and eat!

185
00:14:22,080 --> 00:14:25,220
Also, next time you don't do well, don't waste water.

186
00:14:25,220 --> 00:14:27,150
Here, have some vegetables.

187
00:14:27,150 --> 00:14:29,220
Eat more veggies.

188
00:14:34,020 --> 00:14:36,039
Hurry up.

189
00:14:36,039 --> 00:14:37,279
Huan Er!

190
00:14:37,279 --> 00:14:39,100
- Quick. 
 - Mom, where are we going?

191
00:14:39,100 --> 00:14:42,320
To Aunt Yi Fan's house. She called and invited us over.

192
00:14:42,320 --> 00:14:44,500
By the way, her son goes to Tianhe High School too.

193
00:14:44,500 --> 00:14:45,779
Same age as you.

194
00:14:45,779 --> 00:14:48,300
We'll take this chance to get some study tips.

195
00:14:48,300 --> 00:14:49,500
Hurry up and eat.

196
00:14:49,500 --> 00:14:51,639
Come on, hurry up.

197
00:14:51,639 --> 00:14:52,860
This kid...

198
00:14:52,860 --> 00:14:54,759
Coming.

199
00:14:54,759 --> 00:14:56,600
Yi Fan!

200
00:14:56,600 --> 00:14:57,859
Come on in, sweetie.

201
00:14:57,859 --> 00:14:59,790
What do you have there?

202
00:14:59,790 --> 00:15:03,320
You shouldn't have! No need to be so formal.

203
00:15:03,320 --> 00:15:05,120
Come on. Have a seat.

204
00:15:05,840 --> 00:15:08,200
It's getting late, where's Li Qiang?

205
00:15:08,200 --> 00:15:13,040
He's in a meeting. The Fire Department is always busy.

206
00:15:13,900 --> 00:15:18,019
Son, come out. Aunt Li Na is here.

207
00:15:21,720 --> 00:15:23,919
Xi Chi, right?

208
00:15:23,919 --> 00:15:25,360
Hello, Ma'am.

209
00:15:25,360 --> 00:15:26,879
- You've grown up. 
  - Why is it him again? 

210
00:15:26,879 --> 00:15:28,800
So handsome!

211
00:15:29,919 --> 00:15:32,080
- Today, I brought Huan Er over 
  - I'm speechless. 

212
00:15:32,080 --> 00:15:35,640
to visit. You two must be in the same school.

213
00:15:36,440 --> 00:15:38,340
Why are you standing? Sit down.

214
00:15:38,340 --> 00:15:40,020
Here, have a drink.

215
00:15:42,000 --> 00:15:44,060
Look, he's back from his meeting.

216
00:15:44,060 --> 00:15:46,200
- Speak of the devil. 
 - Jing Xi Chi!

217
00:15:46,200 --> 00:15:50,500
How many times have I told you? Stop leaving your stinky shoes everywhere.

218
00:15:52,440 --> 00:15:54,720
We have guests. How embarrassing!

219
00:15:54,720 --> 00:15:56,000
Li Qiang.

220
00:15:56,000 --> 00:15:57,039
Li Na is here.

221
00:15:57,039 --> 00:15:58,100
Come, Huan Er.

222
00:15:58,100 --> 00:16:00,620
- Say hello. 
 - Hello, sir.

223
00:16:00,620 --> 00:16:02,340
Is she your daughter?

224
00:16:02,340 --> 00:16:04,340
I can hardly recognize her now.

225
00:16:04,340 --> 00:16:06,840
She was so young back then. Hadn't even started primary school yet.

226
00:16:06,840 --> 00:16:08,220
- So many years have passed. 
 - Sit down.

227
00:16:08,220 --> 00:16:11,900
- Sit, sit. 
 - Now, our kids are finally together.

228
00:16:11,900 --> 00:16:15,470
That's right. But if that's the case, don't let our rascal corrupt her.

229
00:16:15,470 --> 00:16:16,720
What nonsense are you talking about?

230
00:16:16,720 --> 00:16:19,640
Like Li Na just said, kids need encouragement.

231
00:16:19,640 --> 00:16:21,600
Li Qiang, you can't talk like that.

232
00:16:21,600 --> 00:16:22,980
They're all good kids.

233
00:16:22,980 --> 00:16:28,119
Today, I brought Huan Er here to learn from Xi Chi.

234
00:16:29,039 --> 00:16:34,239
Since school just started, she's having a little trouble keeping up.

235
00:16:37,140 --> 00:16:40,780
You're asking the wrong person. When it comes to studying, my son—

236
00:16:42,200 --> 00:16:45,000
Let's just say he's good at sports.

237
00:16:45,000 --> 00:16:46,380
Xi Chi, hurry up.

238
00:16:46,380 --> 00:16:49,159
Go to the kitchen and wash the fruit that Aunt Li Na brought us.

239
00:16:49,159 --> 00:16:49,939
All right.

240
00:16:49,939 --> 00:16:53,700
Huan Er, be a good girl and go help him.

241
00:16:53,700 --> 00:16:55,220
I suppose you're staying here for good?

242
00:16:55,220 --> 00:16:56,939
That's right. We're finally together now.

243
00:16:56,939 --> 00:17:00,220
It's good to have someone living in the same complex to rely on.

244
00:17:00,220 --> 00:17:02,919
The knife's over there. Cut it.

245
00:17:03,480 --> 00:17:05,580
Don't forget to wash it first.

246
00:17:07,780 --> 00:17:09,640
Huan Er.

247
00:17:09,640 --> 00:17:11,939
Your eyes look a little swollen.

248
00:17:11,939 --> 00:17:15,460
Don't tell me you cried because you didn't do well on the exam?

249
00:17:16,580 --> 00:17:18,699
- I was just— 
 - No need to explain.

250
00:17:18,699 --> 00:17:20,800
It's fine. Nothing to be ashamed of.

251
00:17:20,800 --> 00:17:24,160
It's just that there's no need to cry over a test.

252
00:17:24,160 --> 00:17:27,219
Want to guess what I scored on my high school entrance exam?

253
00:17:27,219 --> 00:17:29,079
Dead last?

254
00:17:29,620 --> 00:17:31,880
Good guess.

255
00:17:32,480 --> 00:17:36,340
So, just so you know...

256
00:17:36,340 --> 00:17:39,699
I was always a mid-tier student in middle school.

257
00:17:39,699 --> 00:17:41,839
You're already doing great.

258
00:17:46,580 --> 00:17:50,419
You and Qi Qi... are you close friends?

259
00:17:50,419 --> 00:17:52,780
Why are you asking?

260
00:17:54,626 --> 00:17:57,338
You acted like you didn't want to know me at school.

261
00:17:59,200 --> 00:18:02,335
