00:21:01,410 --> 00:21:03,060
You should join too.

305
00:21:03,060 --> 00:21:04,300
I'll think about it.

306
00:21:04,300 --> 00:21:07,460
All right. I'll find some time to list out this semester's key topics.

307
00:21:07,460 --> 00:21:09,480
