311
00:21:19,060 --> 00:21:21,900
Thank you. Thank you, Mr. Song.

312
00:21:21,900 --> 00:21:23,226
No problem.

313
00:21:23,226 --> 00:21:25,540
Isn't my little brother obedient?

314
00:21:26,312 --> 00:21:28,119
