315
00:21:28,119 --> 00:21:29,859
Chen Huan Er!

316
00:21:52,680 --> 00:21:54,200
Qi Qi.

317
00:21:55,340 --> 00:21:56,820
Why are you coming from that way?

318
00:21:56,820 --> 00:21:58,699
I thought you lived in the new district.

319
00:21:58,699 --> 00:22:00,600
Did you move?

320
00:22:02,500 --> 00:22:04,340
You guys...

321
00:22:04,340 --> 00:22:07,500
The three of us live in the same residential compound.

322
00:22:08,340 --> 00:22:09,580
Hello.

323
00:22:09,580 --> 00:22:10,540
- Hello. 
 - Hello.

324
00:22:10,540 --> 00:22:12,660
I'm Qi Qi. Huan Er is my desk mate.

325
