336
00:22:38,060 --> 00:22:41,699
If so, then join us commoners in the regular class.

337
00:22:42,179 --> 00:22:43,400
Not happening.

338
00:22:43,400 --> 00:22:45,790
My grades aren't bad enough.

339
00:22:46,739 --> 00:22:49,460
By the way, my dad just sent these from abroad.

340
00:22:49,460 --> 00:22:52,259
I thought I'd share them with my classmates. Here.

341
00:22:52,259 --> 00:22:54,500
Try one.

342
00:22:54,500 --> 00:22:57,841
Are those Danish butter cookies?

343
00:23:00,219 --> 00:23:01,900
Delicious.

344
00:23:01,900 --> 00:23:03,431
Song Cong, have one too.

345
00:23:03,431 --> 00:23:05,642
I've had them before.

346
00:23:05,642 --> 00:23:07,800
I'm heading off now.

347
00:23:10,700 --> 00:23:12,334
Why is he walking that way?

348
00:23:12,334 --> 00:23:13,754
Didn't you hear me?

349
00:23:13,754 --> 00:23:16,140
He's not an ordinary student. He's in the international program.

350
00:23:16,140 --> 00:23:18,269
His classes are in another building.

351
00:23:19,100 --> 00:23:21,420
