00:24:32,713 --> 00:24:35,173
Math exams don't test pronunciation.

370
00:24:35,173 --> 00:24:37,293
Chen Huan Er, continue.

371
00:24:40,252 --> 00:24:50,632
Equals... B squared plus C squared, minus A squared, divided by 2AB.

