No problem.

377
00:25:14,720 --> 00:25:17,060
Didn't we say we'd study together?

378
00:25:19,140 --> 00:25:20,965
I said I'd think about it.

379
00:25:20,965 --> 00:25:22,560
Stop thinking. You agreed to help Chen Huan Er.

380
00:25:22,560 --> 00:25:26,052
- Hurry up and go study. Come on. 
 - No, I have training later.

381
00:25:26,052 --> 00:25:27,073
I have things to do.

382
00:25:27,073 --> 00:25:28,700
You help her first, okay?

383
00:25:28,700 --> 00:25:30,260
She's struggling with her studies. Help her out. Just go.

384
00:25:30,260 --> 00:25:32,103
Don't come back, just go.

385
00:25:32,103 --> 00:25:33,653
- Help her out, all right? 
 - Fine, carry on.

