Daniel Lin was waiting at the airport.

388
00:25:46,853 --> 00:26:02,580
And her cousin, Liu Qian, went on a trip to Canada to visit their cousins.

389
00:26:02,580 --> 00:26:07,692
A lot of Chinese family...

