00:26:48,240 --> 00:26:50,020
What are you doing?

403
00:26:50,020 --> 00:26:52,380
I'm listening to a recording.

404
00:26:52,380 --> 00:26:54,173
Are you coming up?

405
00:26:54,173 --> 00:26:55,892
Let's go.

406
00:27:03,440 --> 00:27:06,497
- I'll get your shoes. 
 - Oh, thanks.

407
00:27:09,553 --> 00:27:11,333
Have a seat.

408
00:27:11,912 --> 00:27:13,313
Where's Jing Xi Chi?

409
00:27:13,313 --> 00:27:16,020
Why isn't he here yet?

410
00:27:16,020 --> 00:27:18,452
Xi Chi said we'd study together so you wouldn't feel awkward.

411
00:27:18,452 --> 00:27:19,713
He's focused on training.

412
00:27:19,713 --> 00:27:21,913
- He's not coming to study. 
 - What?

413
00:27:23,680 --> 00:27:25,740
Just sit tight for a bit.

414
00:27:31,653 --> 00:27:34,293
Here, this tape is for you.

415
00:27:34,293 --> 00:27:36,532
It should help you a little.

416
00:27:37,173 --> 00:27:39,012
Thanks.

417
