418
00:27:41,292 --> 00:27:44,713
It seems everyone here is so good at English.

419
00:27:46,553 --> 00:27:48,952
We had a head start, that's all.

420
00:27:48,952 --> 00:27:52,153
Practice more, and you'll catch up in no time.

