00:28:56,440 --> 00:28:58,558
I must've taken the wrong one. I need to get it back to him.

435
00:28:58,558 --> 00:29:01,552
- Xiao Yu, here you go. 
 - Thanks.

436
00:29:12,853 --> 00:29:14,192
Song Cong.

437
00:29:14,192 --> 00:29:15,913
Mr. Fu.

438
00:29:16,952 --> 00:29:20,613
Can I skip this competition?

439
00:29:21,592 --> 00:29:23,333
Skip it?

440
00:29:23,333 --> 00:29:25,080
Why?

441
00:29:25,080 --> 00:29:27,760
I've been really busy with schoolwork lately.

442
00:29:28,373 --> 00:29:30,860
Song Cong, stop trying to fool me.

443
00:29:30,860 --> 00:29:32,464
I know you too well.

444
00:29:32,464 --> 00:29:38,340
For an international competition like this, whether it's English or math, besides you,

445
00:29:38,340 --> 00:29:40,173
who else do you think I can send?

446
00:29:40,173 --> 00:29:43,192
Plus, the competitors in this contest are all top-tier.

447
00:29:43,192 --> 00:29:44,933
Don't take it lightly.

448
00:29:44,933 --> 00:29:47,752
Winning first place isn't guaranteed.

449
00:29:49,973 --> 00:29:53,913
Excuse me, is Song Cong in your class?

450
00:29:54,732 --> 00:29:57,993
 Why are the international class students so weird? 

451
00:29:59,520 --> 00:30:01,953
- Excuse me, is Song Cong here? 
 - No idea.

452
00:30:05,853 --> 00:30:07,672
Huan Er.

453
00:30:07,672 --> 00:30:08,793
There you are.

454
00:30:08,793 --> 00:30:10,993
Sorry, I accidentally took your notebook.

455
00:30:10,993 --> 00:30:12,300
I'm sorry for the inconvenience.

456
00:30:12,300 --> 00:30:13,421
It's fine.

457
00:30:13,421 --> 00:30:15,100
- Oh right, today— 
 - Song Cong.

458
00:30:15,100 --> 00:30:17,620
I heard from Mr. Fu that you don't want to participate in the math competition.

459
00:30:17,620 --> 00:30:19,547
Why?

460
00:30:20,214 --> 00:30:22,056
- I just don't want to. 
 - If you don't want to join,

461
00:30:22,056 --> 00:30:24,513
then give me your spot.

462
00:30:31,292 --> 00:30:33,620
What were you about to say?

463
00:30:33,620 --> 00:30:35,733
I wanted to say that I have a test after school today.

464
00:30:35,733 --> 00:30:37,233
I might be half an hour late.

465
00:30:37,233 --> 00:30:39,740
You and Jing Xi Chi should go home without me.

466
00:30:39,740 --> 00:30:41,619
It's fine. We'll wait for you.

467
00:30:41,619 --> 00:30:45,233
How about this? I'll hand in my paper early. You guys wait for me at the back gate.

468
00:30:45,233 --> 00:30:47,413
You can do that?

469
00:30:48,772 --> 00:30:50,352
All right then.

470
00:30:50,972 --> 00:30:52,613
Good.

471
00:31:22,080 --> 00:31:24,872
 Got some fresh gossip about Ms. Kaosign from Class 5. Do you want to hear it? 

472
00:31:24,872 --> 00:31:26,313
Spill it.

473
00:31:26,313 --> 00:31:29,780
She may look all innocent, but she's not that simple.

474
00:31:29,780 --> 00:31:30,785
 How so? 

475
00:31:30,785 --> 00:31:33,349
 She went to the international class this morning to return Song Cong's notebook. 

476
00:31:33,349 --> 00:31:34,513
 For real? 

477
00:31:34,513 --> 00:31:36,140
Why would I lie?

478
00:31:36,140 --> 00:31:40,292
I think she went there on purpose, just to get noticed.

479
00:31:40,292 --> 00:31:42,620
So people would think something is going on between them.

480
00:31:42,620 --> 00:31:45,993
 She's only been here a few days, and she's already hanging out with Qi Qi. 

481
00:31:45,993 --> 00:31:47,672
 Now she's cozying up to Song Cong too. 

482
00:31:47,672 --> 00:31:49,112
 She's definitely not that simple. 

483
00:31:49,112 --> 00:31:52,352
One hand grabs the smart ones, and the other grabs the rich ones.

484
00:31:52,352 --> 00:31:53,780
Who?

485
00:31:53,780 --> 00:31:56,228
Class 5's social butterfly, Ms. Kaosign.

486
00:31:56,228 --> 00:31:57,353
The new girl in Class 5?

487
00:31:57,353 --> 00:31:59,740
 Doesn't stand out at all, but turns out she's a socialite? 

488
00:31:59,740 --> 00:32:01,963
 That's why she's impressive. 

489
00:32:01,963 --> 00:32:05,740
No wonder the area outside the bathroom smells worse than inside.

490
00:32:05,740 --> 00:32:07,713
 Turns out it's because some people have filthy mouths. 

491
00:32:07,713 --> 00:32:10,813
What do you mean? Who are you talking about?

492
00:32:12,473 --> 00:32:15,452
I'm talking about you, Class 6 guys.

493
00:32:15,452 --> 00:32:19,752
Not everyone is as dark-hearted as you.

494
00:32:26,853 --> 00:32:28,573
Jing Xi Chi.

495
00:32:28,573 --> 00:32:31,112
Stop looking for trouble here.

496
00:32:34,492 --> 00:32:37,413
I am looking for trouble today.

497
00:32:37,413 --> 00:32:38,972
What about it?

498
00:32:40,993 --> 00:32:43,532
Chen Huan Er is my friend.

499
00:32:46,133 --> 00:32:49,473
Next time you gossip behind her back,

500
00:32:51,492 --> 00:32:53,352
think twice.

501
00:32:54,212 --> 00:32:56,452
Why are you acting so arrogant?

502
00:33:05,012 --> 00:33:07,112
Try touching me again.

503
00:33:07,112 --> 00:33:09,833
Jing Xi Chi, is this really necessary?

504
00:33:09,833 --> 00:33:11,672
We were just casually talking.

505
00:33:11,672 --> 00:33:16,100
Qin Liang, keep your classmates' mouths in check.

506
00:33:16,100 --> 00:33:20,833
You should spend more time practicing instead of getting dominated by me on the soccer field,

507
00:33:20,833 --> 00:33:23,073
then trying to act tough at school.

508
00:33:23,073 --> 00:33:24,540
Forget it, Qin Liang.

509
00:33:24,540 --> 00:33:26,772
Let's not lower ourselves to Class 5's level.

510
00:33:26,772 --> 00:33:29,433
- Let's go. 
 - Yeah.

511
00:34:00,920 --> 00:34:04,839
You heard everything just now, didn't you?

512
00:34:12,740 --> 00:34:15,560
You're not crying in the bathroom, are you?

513
00:34:16,912 --> 00:34:21,293
