514
00:34:22,572 --> 00:34:24,132
Impressive.

515
00:34:25,153 --> 00:34:26,512
Don't believe me?

516
00:34:26,512 --> 00:34:29,153
- My dad is a martial arts coach. 
 - Impressive.

517
00:34:29,153 --> 00:34:30,953
