00:34:45,500 --> 00:34:47,380
I'm fine.

523
00:34:47,380 --> 00:34:48,597
It's all because of you.

524
00:34:48,597 --> 00:34:50,780
You must be the last person to leave the school.

525
00:34:50,780 --> 00:34:52,713
What? All my classmates are still here.

526
00:34:52,713 --> 00:34:55,092
- What are they doing? 
 - Comparing answers.

527
00:34:55,092 --> 00:34:57,653
They're already checking the answers right after finishing the test?

528
00:34:57,653 --> 00:34:59,700
Just my answers.

529
00:34:59,700 --> 00:35:01,299
So arrogant...

530
00:35:03,200 --> 00:35:04,401
You guys are such good friends.

531
00:35:04,401 --> 00:35:07,193
How come one of you is a top student and the other a slacker?

532
00:35:07,193 --> 00:35:11,912
Didn't Darwin say we should respect species diversity?

533
00:35:11,912 --> 00:35:13,740
Darwin never said that.

534
00:35:13,740 --> 00:35:15,198
I'm not arguing with you.

535
00:35:15,198 --> 00:35:18,033
I'm off to training. You two be careful.

536
00:35:23,213 --> 00:35:26,313
Did the tape I gave you help at all?

537
00:35:26,972 --> 00:35:30,052
Yeah. Thanks.

538
00:35:30,052 --> 00:35:32,533
How are you adjusting to Tianhe?

539
00:35:34,172 --> 00:35:36,372
Not bad.

540
00:35:37,633 --> 00:35:40,353
Just now Xi Chi said I need to make it up to you.

541
00:35:40,353 --> 00:35:42,060
Did I really keep you waiting too long?

542
00:35:42,060 --> 00:35:45,546
No. Don't listen to his nonsense.

543
00:35:45,546 --> 00:35:48,253
Let's continue tutoring after dinner.

544
00:35:49,040 --> 00:35:50,762
No need for now.

545
00:35:50,762 --> 00:35:52,593
I don't want to trouble you.

546
00:35:55,153 --> 00:35:57,253
I'll head home now.

547
00:36:15,912 --> 00:36:18,072
I'm home.

548
00:36:36,313 --> 00:36:38,153
 I have to work overtime today. 

549
00:36:38,153 --> 00:36:40,912
 I've arranged with Aunt Hao. You can have dinner at her place. 

550
00:36:40,912 --> 00:36:44,152
 Let me know when you're home. 

551
00:36:59,172 --> 00:37:01,392
Hello? Dad?

552
00:37:02,572 --> 00:37:04,293
What's the matter?

553
00:37:08,773 --> 00:37:10,460
Yes, I've had my dinner.

554
00:37:10,460 --> 00:37:14,313
Don't worry. Everything is going well here.

555
00:37:15,827 --> 00:37:17,532
My classmates?

556
00:37:17,532 --> 00:37:19,893
They're all pretty nice to me.

557
00:37:19,893 --> 00:37:22,293
All right, let's stop here for now. I need to do my homework.

558
00:37:22,293 --> 00:37:24,012
Bye-bye.

559
00:37:29,333 --> 00:37:30,872
Song Cong.

560
00:37:30,872 --> 00:37:33,593
Send a message to Huan Er: ask her to come over for dinner.

561
00:37:33,593 --> 00:37:35,092
Aunt Li Na is working late today.

562
00:37:35,092 --> 00:37:36,772
All right.

563
00:37:42,092 --> 00:37:45,933
 Huan Er, your mother wants you to come over for dinner. 

564
00:37:49,572 --> 00:37:52,173
 I've already eaten. I won't come over. 

565
00:37:52,173 --> 00:37:53,293
   

566
00:37:53,293 --> 00:37:55,673
   

567
00:38:08,713 --> 00:38:13,353
♫  I remember some beautiful things  ♫

568
00:38:14,400 --> 00:38:15,733
Mom.

569
00:38:15,733 --> 00:38:18,452
She said she already ate. She won't be coming.

570
00:38:18,452 --> 00:38:20,273
What did she eat? This girl...

571
00:38:20,273 --> 00:38:24,813
♫  But happiness fades too fast  ♫

572
00:38:24,813 --> 00:38:27,452
Come on, eat up.

573
00:38:27,452 --> 00:38:29,393
Not coming, right?

574
00:38:32,633 --> 00:38:39,713
♫  It has arrived, there's nowhere to escape anyway  ♫

575
00:38:39,713 --> 00:38:46,753
♫  It has arrived, well... inexplicably  ♫

576
00:38:46,753 --> 00:38:51,313
♫  I don't want to speak or eat  ♫

577
00:39:00,760 --> 00:39:02,133
Hello.

578
00:39:02,133 --> 00:39:04,573
 Where are you? 

579
00:39:05,893 --> 00:39:07,452
I'm at home.

580
00:39:07,452 --> 00:39:08,572
 Liar. 

581
00:39:08,572 --> 00:39:10,933
 The lights aren't even on. 

582
00:39:12,440 --> 00:39:14,720
What's the matter? Why are you calling me?

583
00:39:14,720 --> 00:39:18,753
 Song Cong told me you seemed a little depressed after school, 

584
00:39:18,753 --> 00:39:22,153
 so I thought I'd call and check to make sure you're okay. 

585
00:39:22,813 --> 00:39:23,813
Yeah.

586
00:39:23,813 --> 00:39:26,800
Right now, I'm standing on top of the hospital building.

587
00:39:26,800 --> 00:39:28,933
Looking down, it's pretty spacious. The height is just right.

588
00:39:28,933 --> 00:39:32,693
It's perfect for jumping off.

589
00:39:33,893 --> 00:39:35,333
 Don't jump off yet. 

590
00:39:35,333 --> 00:39:38,972
 I need to let my dad and the others know so they can prepare for the rescue. 

591
00:39:38,972 --> 00:39:40,733
I'm fine, really.

592
00:39:40,733 --> 00:39:41,933
Don't worry.

593
00:39:41,933 --> 00:39:43,813
 I know you're fine. 

594
00:39:43,813 --> 00:39:47,132
 But look at you, after just a few laps, you're already this exhausted. 

595
00:39:47,132 --> 00:39:50,632
Your physical fitness is seriously lacking.

596
00:39:56,813 --> 00:39:59,000
- What are you doing here? 
 - What am I doing here?

597
00:39:59,000 --> 00:40:01,406
Are you kidding? This is my turf.

598
00:40:01,406 --> 00:40:03,493
I've just finished my practice.

599
00:40:06,813 --> 00:40:09,532
Anyway, about what happened today...

600
00:40:09,532 --> 00:40:11,393
Thank you.

601
00:40:11,960 --> 00:40:13,761
You're my little brother.

602
00:40:13,761 --> 00:40:15,532
Who else would I look out for?

603
00:40:15,532 --> 00:40:18,112
Fine, I owe you one then.

604
00:40:24,333 --> 00:40:26,072
Have you eaten?

605
00:40:27,193 --> 00:40:28,593
I have.

606
00:40:28,593 --> 00:40:30,072
I ate a ton.

607
00:40:30,072 --> 00:40:34,532
- I was just having my post-meal run. 
 - No, you haven't.

608
00:40:34,532 --> 00:40:36,933
Fine. I'm feeling generous today.

609
00:40:36,933 --> 00:40:38,972
I'll take you somewhere nice.

610
00:40:38,972 --> 00:40:40,253
Where?

611
00:40:40,253 --> 00:40:41,452
Just follow me, you'll see.

612
00:40:41,452 --> 00:40:43,083
If you don't tell me, I'm not going.

613
00:40:43,083 --> 00:40:44,813
Come with me, and I'll tell you.

614
00:40:44,813 --> 00:40:46,713
Such a tease.

615
00:40:46,713 --> 00:40:48,363
Come on, this way.

616
00:40:57,213 --> 00:40:59,172
Where are you taking me?

617
00:40:59,172 --> 00:41:02,093
Almost there. You'll know soon enough.

