♫  Before saying goodbye  ♫ 
 ♫  The you from back then  ♫

630
00:42:27,153 --> 00:42:31,873
♫  Still free and passionate  ♫

631
00:42:31,873 --> 00:42:35,333
♫  If only this summer could last a little longer  ♫

