00:42:49,493 --> 00:42:54,433
♫  Walk a little slower  ♫ 
 ♫  The us from back then  ♫

636
00:42:54,433 --> 00:42:58,123
♫  Still didn't know how to tell things apart  ♫

637
00:42:59,033 --> 00:43:02,663
♫  In my memories, sweat dampened your face  ♫

638
00:43:02,663 --> 00:43:06,073
♫  Still shining just as brightly  ♫

639
00:43:06,073 --> 00:43:12,253
♫  Looking forward to the day  ♫ 
 ♫  When we meet again  ♫

640
00:43:12,253 --> 00:43:17,653
♫  At the right time  ♫

